An evening of exceptional brilliance at Pride of Tanishq, Mumbai.

From an immersive journey of natural diamond evolution to an intimate masterclass on the brightest sparkling diamonds of Tanishq, our beloved Mumbaikars experienced the extraordinary. The crescendo? A magnificent showcase of the latest Rivaah x Tarun Tahiliani collection, where the modernity in our heritage was celebrated on the runway.

To our distinguished guests - thank you for being part of this rare celebration.
